column2: select so.bossprimary, so.sdssprimary, sp.specObjID, sp.objid, so.specObjID, so.mjd, so.plate, so.fiberID, sp.ra,sp.dec,sp.z,so.z_noqso,so.zErr_noqso, sp.class,sp.subclass,so.class_noqso,so.subclass_noqso,so.class_person,   so.programname,so.instrument,so.survey,so.scienceprimary, so.zwarning,so.zwarning_noqso, so.boss_target1, so.eboss_target1, so.snmedian, sp.cmodelmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS cmod_u, sp.cmodelmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS cmod_g, sp.cmodelmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS cmod_r, sp.cmodelmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS cmod_i, sp.cmodelmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS cmod_z, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS psf_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS psf_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS psf_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS psf_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS psf_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak,f.integr,f.rms into mydb.MyTable from SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN SpecObj as so ON sp.specobjid = so.specobjid JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid   JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr   WHERE (sp.cmodelmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #)
